        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Problem: Dreaming module diary UI had hardcoded English strings and incomplete Chinese translations (restartConfirmation was still in English).\n- Why it matters: Non-English users see mixed-language UI in the Dreaming tab.\n- What changed: Extracted all hardcoded strings from `ui/src/ui/views/dreaming.ts` into i18n keys, added translations to both `en.ts` and `zh-CN.ts`, and completed the restartConfirmation Chinese translations.\n- What did NOT change (scope boundary): No functional behavior, logic, or styling changed. No new features added. No other locales touched.\n\n## Change Type (select all)\n\n- [ ] Bug fix\n- [ ] Feature\n- [ ] Refactor required for the fix\n- [ ] Docs\n- [ ] Security hardening\n- [x] Chore/infra\n\n## Scope (select all touched areas)\n\n- [ ] Gateway / orchestration\n- [ ] Skills / tool execution\n- [ ] Auth / tokens\n- [ ] Memory / storage\n- [ ] Integrations\n- [ ] API / contracts\n- [x] UI / DX\n- [ ] CI/CD / infra\n\n## Linked Issue/PR\n\n- Closes #\n- Related #\n- [ ] This PR fixes a bug or regression\n\n## Real behavior proof (required for external PRs)\n\n- Behavior or issue addressed: Dreaming module UI strings were not fully localized to Simplified Chinese.\n- Real environment tested: Local dev gateway (`pnpm gateway:dev`).\n- Exact steps or command run after this patch: Built UI assets with `pnpm ui:build`, started gateway, opened Control UI Dreaming tab.\n- Evidence after fix: Screenshot — Diary subtab labels (梦境日记 / 导入洞察 / 记忆宫殿), explainer paragraphs, and Memory Wiki hints all render in Chinese.\n\n  ![after](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/06c2580e-3c35-4377-886b-72d35f28900c)\n- Observed result after fix: zh-CN locale shows fully translated Dreaming diary UI.\n- What was not tested: Other non-English locales.\n\n## Root Cause (if applicable)\n\nN/A — not a bug fix.\n\n## Regression Test Plan (if applicable)\n\nN/A — not a bug fix or regression.\n\n## User-visible / Behavior Changes\n\n- Dreaming module diary UI now fully localized to Simplified Chinese (zh-CN).\n- English locale unchanged (new keys added, existing behavior preserved).\n\n## Diagram (if applicable)\n\nN/A\n\n## Security Impact (required)\n\n- New permissions/capabilities? (`No`)\n- Secrets/tokens handling changed? (`No`)\n- New/changed network calls? (`No`)\n- Command/tool execution surface changed? (`No`)\n- Data access scope changed? (`No`)\n- If any `Yes`, explain risk + mitigation:\n\n## Repro + Verification\n\n### Environment\n\n- OS: macOS\n- Runtime/container: Node 22 (local dev)\n- Model/provider: N/A\n- Integration/channel (if any): N/A\n- Relevant config (redacted): N/A\n\n### Steps\n\n1. `pnpm ui:build` to build Control UI assets\n2. `pnpm gateway:dev` to start local gateway\n3. Open Control UI in browser, navigate to Dreaming tab\n4. Switch locale to zh-CN (if not already)\n5. Toggle Dreaming mode to trigger restart confirmation dialog\n\n### Expected\n\n- Diary subtab labels display in Chinese: 梦境日记, 导入洞察, 记忆宫殿\n- Explainer paragraphs display in Chinese\n- Memory Wiki unavailable hints display in Chinese\n- Restart confirmation dialog displays in Chinese\n\n### Actual\n\n- All above verified locally.\n\n## Evidence\n\n- [ ] Failing test/log before + passing after\n- [ ] Trace/log snippets\n- [x] Screenshot/recording\n- [ ] Perf numbers (if relevant)\n\n**Before**\n<img width=\"2464\" height=\"844\" alt=\"1\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8128f4b4-d731-4bbb-ae24-8fbc2c657aa1\"/>\n<img width=\"1792\" height=\"756\" alt=\"2\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bf7157bc-0d75-473d-8270-1572842b843a\"/>\n\n**After**\n<img width=\"2500\" height=\"600\" alt=\"3\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/06c2580e-3c35-4377-886b-72d35f28900c\"/>\n<img width=\"1878\" height=\"822\" alt=\"4\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/0eedc582-af73-47bc-b93f-1d79dbcc9bee\"/>\n\n\n## Human Verification (required)\n\n- Verified scenarios: Dreaming tab diary subtabs, explainer text, Memory Wiki hints, restart confirmation dialog in zh-CN locale.\n- Edge cases checked: English locale still renders correctly (new keys added to en.ts).\n- What you did **not** verify: Other non-English locales.\n\n## Review Conversations\n\n- [x] I replied to or resolved every bot review conversation I addressed in this PR.\n- [x] I left unresolved only the conversations that still need reviewer or maintainer judgment.\n\n## Compatibility / Migration\n\n- Backward compatible? (`Yes`)\n- Config/env changes? (`No`)\n- Migration needed? (`No`)\n- If yes, exact upgrade steps:\n\n## Risks and Mitigations\n\nNone.",
